official_title: A bill to transfer jurisdiction to the District Court for the District of Alaska for claims for attorney and consultant fees and out-of-pocket expenses pursuant to section 20 (b), (c) and (d) of the Alaska Native Claims Settlement Act, Public Law 92-203.

summary.text: Transfers jurisdiction to the District Court for the District of Alaska for claims for attorney and consultant fees and out-of-pocket expenses pursuant to the Alaska Native Claims Settlement Act.
